howtoplay.desc.message: To enter the game, you need to roll a 6 on the dice. The player rolls the dice, allowing the forces of karma to determine his next position on the board. He passes through the various planes of existence, ascending with arrows and descending with snakes, striving to comprehend the intention of his Higher Self wherever he goes.

bonusDescription.message: Creator of the mobile game Leela Chakra Ai with a personal Guru assistant, entered the TOP 100 educational mobile gaming platforms by App Store.

description.message: Consultation with neurocoach Gaia Kamskaya with 12 years of experience in Vedic culture as a teacher and creator of the mobile game Leela Chakra Ai - NeuroLila, with a personal Guru assistant, entered the TOP 100 educational mobile gaming platforms by App Store. Gaia is a spiritual mentor, Vedic researcher, and Jnana Yoga teacher. She holds the status of Brahmacari in the tradition of Advaita Vedanta - the path of non-duality, whose roots go back to Datta Treya, the creator of the Vedas. Harmoniously combining ancient wisdom and modern technologies, Gaia opens a new era of self-discovery. Her mission is to help people understand their true nature, achieve inner integrity, and learn to mix ancient Vedic knowledge and technologies in real life.

consultationBenefits.message: Benefits of consultation: personal support, long-term effect, formation of intention, unpacking of personality, discussion of personal goals/ambitions and development of a strategy for their achievement, both professional and personal growth, tools and techniques for managing emotions, as well as psychological aspects of one's life, self-assessment, motivation, inspiration, and relationships.
